description:
In this Karaoke with Lyrics video, we'll be singing over the beautiful sunset from the top of Over the Sunset Mountain. This video is perfect for those warm summer nights, and you'll love the key of D & E!

Title: Over the Sunset Mountains
Author: John W. Peterson
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Youtube Production.
